{"tid":2103664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本可能繼續建立陸基神盾 抵禦北韓及中國攻擊","createTime":"2020-07-11T11:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T11:48:11.000Z","uid":75656,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ce1bad1e5eaa8a545eb692980d7d75425be1c906","tid":2103664,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:10:30.000Z","msg":"路透社引述消息人士獨家報導，日本仍可能繼續建立「陸基神盾」(Aegis Ashore)飛彈防衛系統，以抵禦北韓及其他區域敵人的攻擊，包括中國在內。<br />\n<br />\n日本防衛大臣河野太郎(Taro Kono)上月取消建立兩座「陸基神盾」系統雷達站的計畫，他提及成本及安全顧慮，因為從攔截飛彈脫離的推進器可能砸中地方居民。<br />\n<br />\n然而，日本尚未取消與洛克希德馬丁公司(Lockheed Martin)建立「陸基神盾」防空雷達的10億美元合約。<br />\n<br />\n知情消息人士透露，日本正仔細考慮來自美國政府的一項技術評估，這項評估建議使用會排除安全問題的其他地點。<br />\n<br />\n日本堅持使用「陸基神盾」的任何決定，都可能令北京及莫斯科當局感到不安，中俄兩國強烈要求終止這項部署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2071608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2071608&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=cd3bcf2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2071608</a>"},{"pid":"e6aa7b15d5f752736e491725eed8a73198b69030","tid":2103664,"uid":225422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f47ac5524807d5b79dc2447f58e1c57441ae5b","tid":2103664,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bf1b3f234e4f159a78bfc09be7fc81df6221eb","tid":2103664,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:48:11.000Z","msg":"人地防衛都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}